gw.entity

Class IEntityType

  • gw.entity.IEntityType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompilable, IEnhanceableType, com.guidewire.pl.system.entity.external.IExternalType, IFileBasedType, IFileRepositoryBasedType, IJavaBackedType, IType

    public class IEntityType
implements IType, IEnhanceableType, IJavaBackedType, ICompilable, com.guidewire.pl.system.entity.external.IExternalType, IFileRepositoryBasedType, IFileBasedType
    A marker interface for entity types. This is used for persistance layer type safty

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      java.util.List<IEntityType> AllSubtypes
      Returns all entity types that derrive form this entity type. This list does not include the current type.
      java.util.Iterator<com.guidewire.commons.entity.type2.IEntityPropInfoInternal> EntityProperties
      Returns all properties that implement the IEntityPropertyInfo interface
      java.util.List<IEntityType> ImmediateSubtypes
      Returns a list of immediate subtypes of the current object. This method will not recurse down the subtype tree.
      boolean Retireable
      Returns true if this type is retireable. Retireable beans do not get deleted from the database. Instead an aditional column is added to the table, of type boolean, that tracks if the row is no longer "desireable". Retired rows are not returned from queries of any type.
      IEntityType RootType
      Returns the root type for this entity. The root type is the base type for an entity in it's hierarchy. I.e. the table type for the entity.
      com.guidewire.commons.typelist.SubtypeKey SubtypeTypeKey
      Returns the typekey for this subtype type. If this object isn't (or doesn't have) subtypes then this returns null. NOTE: base types will have a typekey iff that type has subtypes as well.
      boolean Versionable
      Returns true if this type is versionable. A versionable type will have a version number automatically added to every bean. Specifically an additional column will be added to the DB table to track versioning of each bean.
